elements.name: Upload PO files and validate PO Details

steps.name: Verify success message "L_O_LNS_PO.A877CB7D.A015A041.xml File is uploaded successfully"
Click on Upload File List available on the side bar
Select "PO" from File Type drop down
Verify the status "Completed.." of the uploaded file "L_O_LNS_PO.A877CB7D.A015A041.xml"
Verify the PO Details in the Result grid "SS7513355"
